==================================================
1) Merge hotfix to master
==================================================
	
	$ git checkout master
	$ git merge hotfix

	This merges the hotfix branch into master branch moves the HEAD pointer ahead.(Fast Forward)

==================================================
2) Merge issuebranch to (new hotfix) master
==================================================
	
	$ git checkout master
	$ git merge issuebranch

	Recursive strategy is used to merge two branches in this case new merge commit branch is created based on the commits in two or different branches.

==================================================
3) Delete Branch
==================================================
	
	$ git branch -d <branchname>

	This merges the hotfix branch into master branch moves the HEAD pointer ahead.(Fast Forward)